frames.caption: A divine figure, wearing a crown of thorns and a radiant halo, embraces a man in a torn shirt. Surrounding them are angelic figures with wings, hands clasped in prayer. The scene is illuminated with a warm, heavenly glow.
frames.description: The scene depicts a spiritual and comforting moment, where a divine figure offers solace to a man. This is set in a celestial environment, with angels present, enhancing the sacred atmosphere.
